Source: anagramarama
Section: games
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Mauro Lizaur <mauro@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), libsdl1.2-dev (>= 1.2.15-5), libsdl-mixer1.2-dev (>= 1.2.12-2), dpkg-dev (>= 1.16.1~), quilt
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Homepage: https://github.com/Anagramarama/anagramarama

Package: anagramarama
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, anagramarama-data (= ${source:Version})
Description: Multi-platform, multi-lingual anagram finding game
 Anagram game, supports various languages and allows the player 
 to play anagrams.
 It detects automatically the language and uses a wordlist according
 to the one defined in the users' session.
 .
 This package is part of the meta package 'conectar-apps-distro'.

Package: anagramarama-data
Architecture: all
Replaces: anagramarama (<= 0.4-4)
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Multi-platform, multi-lingual anagram finding game
 Anagram game, supports various languages and allows the player 
 to play anagrams.
 It detects automatically the language and uses a wordlist according
 to the one defined in the users' session.
 .
 This package contains the data files for anagramarama.
